=== 0.3.0 (8 March 2013) ===
* Heroics Mode is now beta!
* Added level-up equipment and shop, as well as another shop, to HM
* Some HM balancing
* Added some limits and dependencies
* Added amp-tags to comments (see DEV_README)
* HM versions of Hidden Valley, Auction-X, and Isar's Cross
* Completely redid Hidden Valley, as it was un-salvagably asymmetrical.
* Added CHANGELOG, DEV_README, and lua_howto.html
* Added images to the improvement and help menus

